    <innerclass refid="classStmGpio" prot="public">StmGpio</innerclass>
    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 GPIO wrapper — full HAL integration with EXTI interrupt support. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Users configure GPIO pins in STM32CubeMX, then use this wrapper to provide the <ref refid="classBaseGpio" kindref="compound">BaseGpio</ref> interface. Runtime direction/pull/output-mode changes re-apply HAL_GPIO_Init. EXTI interrupts are routed through a static dispatch table.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="author"><para>HardFOC </para>
</simplesect>
